<?php include 'includes/mygooey.php'; ?><div class="e-rel" id="barba-wrapper" data-barba="wrapper" data-scroll><div class="barba-container page-about e-wp" data-barba="container" data-barba-namespace="about" data-namespace="about" data-current="" data-scroll-content><header class="header-about e-rel"><div class="all-projects e-abs"><a href="<?php echo get_site_url(); ?>" data-to="home"><button class="page__close e-rel e-curp bd-black"><span class="t-black e-sans t-switch">BACK</span></button></a></div><div class="header-about__title e-hold"><h1 class="t-switch">You&rsquo;re interested. I&rsquo;m blushing.</h1></div></header><main><div class="about-me e-hold"><p class="headshot"><img src="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/images/jaslin-tonton-headshot.png" alt="headshot"></p><div class="copy"><h2 class="t-switch animate">Jaslin Tonton Digital Designer &amp; Storyteller. </h2><p class="t-switch-gray animate">As a designer, I love simplifying complex problems and telling engaging stories. I believe the most innovative solution to a complex problem is often the simplest. I bring together my years of design and life experience to help people and brands tell their&nbsp;stories.</p></div></div><section class="beginning e-hold callout"><p class="mini-heading t-switch animate-single">In the beginning</p><h3 class="lg-heading t-switch animate">Made in Haiti. Designed in Orlando.</h3><div class="copy"><p class="t-switch-gray animate">Born and raised in Haiti until the age of 13. Then I moved to the states, where my design journey begins. Designed my first MySpace page and thought, &lsquo;Hey, this design thing is pretty easy.&rsquo; Ah, the blissful ignorance of&nbsp;youth.</p><p class="t-switch-gray animate">Much <del>older</del> <ins>wiser</ins> and humbler now, living in the sunshine state, where I&rsquo;m crafting, directing, and perfecting my skills daily as a <b>Creative Director</b> at <b>Very Big&nbsp;Things</b>.</p></div></section><section class="process e-hold three-col-block"><p class="mini-heading t-switch animate-single">My process</p><h3 class="lg-heading t-switch animate">How it all comes together.</h3><ul><li><p class="t-switch"><strong class="t-switch animate-single">Learning</strong><q class="t-switch animate">Listen to understand, not just to&nbsp;answer.</q></p><p class="t-switch-gray animate">Understanding the user&rsquo;s needs and the product&rsquo;s objectives are my first steps to solving any&nbsp;problem.</p></li><li><p class="t-switch"><strong class="t-switch animate-single">Thinking</strong><q class="t-switch animate">Think of many things&mdash;do&nbsp;one.</q></p><p class="t-switch-gray animate">I set aside all assumptions and approach each project with an open mind. Hypothesize, ideate, test, and&nbsp;reiterate.</p></li><li><p class="t-switch"><strong class="t-switch animate-single">Creating</strong><q class="t-switch animate">Beauty is a good letter of&nbsp;introduction.</q></p><p class="t-switch-gray animate">You cannot have an incredible user experience without great aesthetics. It's all in the balance. I spend endless time stressing the small details because they&nbsp;matter.</p></li></ul></section><section class="interlude e-white"><div class="e-hold callout"><p class="mini-heading t-switch-a animate-single">Interlude</p><h3 class="lg-heading t-switch-a animate">Much more than design.</h3><div class="copy"><p class="t-switch-gray animate">Being a designer is important, but more than that I truly value my family&mdash;being a husband and a father is my greatest&nbsp;achievement. </p><p class="t-switch-gray animate">When I'm not busy telling digital stories, you&rsquo;ll find me &lsquo;bending it like Beckham&rsquo; at the soccer field or watching Moana for the 88th time with my wife and&nbsp;daughters.</p><p class="t-switch"><q class="animate">&ldquo;Hire him&mdash;he&rsquo;s a good son. He calls, and not just on holidays.&rdquo;</q><cite class="animate-single">Mom</cite></p></div></div></section><section class="wrapup e-black callout"><p class="mini-heading t-switch animate-single">I love what I do</p><h3 class="lg-heading t-switch animate">Time flies when I&rsquo;m designing.</h3><div class="copy"><p class="t-switch-gray"><strong class="years t-switch animate-years"><?php echo date('Y') - 2011; ?> <span class="img-mask"><img class="emoji" src="<?php echo get_template_directory_uri(); ?>/images/computer-emoji-black.png" alt="headshot"></span></strong> <span class="animate">years of learning, thinking, creating, and telling compelling stories for companies and individuals&nbsp;worldwide.</span></p><p class="t-switch-gray animate">I&rsquo;ve succeeded and failed at times. But I have never failed to learn from my experiences. I look forward to the next 10 years with glee and gladness in my&nbsp;heart.</p></div></section></main><?php include 'includes/myfooter.php'; ?></div></div></body></html>